      <title>尽管电动汽车增长放缓，VinFast 仍继续推进亚洲扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/vinfast-pushes-ahead-with-asia-expansion-even-as-ev-growth-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南电动汽车制造商 VinFast Auto Ltd. 正在大力推进亚洲市场的扩张，其创始人 Pham Nhat Vuong 并未因全球电动汽车需求放缓以及公司进军美国市场的不温不火而受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/vinfast-pushes-ahead-with-asia-expansion-even-as-ev-growth-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 07:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
